Class CheatingAgent

java.lang.Object
  testbed.agent.Agent
      testbed.participants.CheatingAgent

public class CheatingAgent
extends Agent

Cheating agent: always promises reputations and opinions, but never sends them, all weights = 1.0 never requests reputations because it never uses them

Author:
K. Fullam, Jomi F. Hubner
